00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:53.710
&gt;&gt; Kiersten White: So every country
has their own amazing intricate

00:24:53.710 --> 00:24:56.590
history and there was a Hungarian
leader named John Hunyadi

00:24:56.590 --> 00:25:00.430 position:56%
